    Verify Ping Is Successful    ${output}
    Wait Until Keyword Succeeds    30s    5s    L2GatewayOperations.Verify Ping In Namespace Extra Timeout    ${HWVTEP_NS2}    ${BM_PORT2_MAC}    ${port_ip_list[1]}
